articles.title: European Commission to partly boycott Hungary's presidency - DW (English)
articles.description: Brussels has reacted to Viktor Orban's "peace mission" to Moscow by snubbing Hungary's six months as European Council president. It will only send civil servants, not Commissioners, to meetings chaired by Hungary.
